				<td colspan="2"><span>As an alternative - 
<br />

<br />
1-5 Tutorial Zone (1 hour'ish)
<br />

<br />
5-8 Steamfont - Kill the Kolbolts, there not social and drop pelts worth 8gp and Springwater whichs sells in the Bazaar for a few plat.
<br />

<br />
8-12 Butchblock - Pick a goblin camp (one without casters) Lull and pull.  Good xp and great plat (heads and blood sell for 4+ plat to vendors)
<br />

<br />
12-18 Kurns Tower - I personnaly hate PC so go here instead. It has the same xp mod as PC but imo is a much nicer zone.
<br />

<br />
Thats it for the moment <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
